asset.title: Make it Count Southwest Tour 2015
asset.description: Join Levi Brown, Donny Barley, Chad Tim Tim, and the Make It Count crew as they head through the Southwest throwing skate contests for local communities to find the new generation of kids out there. From contests in Phoenix to Albuquerque to Austin, it’s nothin’ but good times for Make It Count. Look out for more MIC coverage in the coming weeks, see you at next one!
asset.author: Element Brand
